Miseratus fonte Ditis conubia.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title/><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/movie/details/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/movie/details/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="details">
 Details
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#details">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Details shortcode is a helper for &lt;code>details&lt;/code> html5 element. It is going to replace &lt;code>expand&lt;/code> shortcode.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="example">
 Example
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#example">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
